snippet.title: Bionic Bay - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Bionic Bay is an action-packed, precision platformer with intricate pixel art, physics-based platforming challenges, and a central swap mechanic. Hop into this latest feature and get a peek into the newly unveiled: the ability to control time, harness gravity, teleport, and race with others’ ghosts.

The world of Bionic Bay is mysterious and packed with secrets waiting to be found. It lands onto Steam &  PS5 on 13th March next year. 

Wishlist now:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1928690/Bionic_Bay/
PS5: https://store.playstation.com/fi-fi/concept/10011377/
